-- MOVES-PricewaterhouseCoopers U.S. names new industry leaders
-- 
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 03:32PM EDT
-- None



Oct 16 (Reuters) - PricewaterhouseCoopers' [PWC.UL] U.S. division said it appointed Charles Marx, Pamela Schlosser, Mike Tomera and Jennifer Fahey as new industry leaders within the company's Industrial Products practice, effective immediately.

Marx will serve as Aerospace and Defense (A&D) leader, while Schlosser will serve as Chemicals leader.